{"id":"cc-skills-i97.1","title":"Add configuration support (env + .claude/skills.config.json)","description":"Implement configuration management for skillsctl. Support environment variables for overrides and .codex/skills.config.json for persistent project-level configuration. Configuration should include: default registry URL, trusted sources, skill aliases, and other CLI settings.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:38.101877+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:49.025501+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.1","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:38.104105+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
{"id":"cc-skills-i97.10","title":"Implement remove command","description":"Implement the 'skillsctl remove \u003cskill\u003e' command to uninstall skills from the project. Clean up submodule entries, sparse-checkout patterns, and manifest entries. Handle dirty state detection and provide --force flag. Support removing multiple skills at once.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:06.518331+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:06.518331+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.10","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:06.519865+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
{"id":"cc-skills-i97.11","title":"Implement set command","description":"Implement the 'skillsctl set \u003ckey\u003e \u003cvalue\u003e' command to configure skills and CLI settings. Support setting skill-specific options, global CLI preferences, and project-level configuration. Persist changes to appropriate config files (.codex/skills.config.json or skill-specific config).","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:07.792035+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:07.792035+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.11","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:07.793327+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
{"id":"cc-skills-i97.12","title":"Implement sync command","description":"Implement the 'skillsctl sync' command to synchronize skill state. Update submodules to configured refs, ensure sparse-checkout patterns are correct, validate manifest consistency, and report any discrepancies. Support --dry-run to preview changes.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:09.156088+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:09.156088+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.12","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:09.157541+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
{"id":"cc-skills-i97.13","title":"Implement status command","description":"Implement the 'skillsctl status' command to show current skill installation state. Display installed skills, their versions, source repos, and health status. Show pending updates if available. Indicate any configuration issues or sync problems.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:10.199504+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:10.199504+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.13","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:10.201205+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
{"id":"cc-skills-i97.2","title":"Implement manifest management (.claude/skills.manifest)","description":"Implement manifest file management for tracking installed skills. The manifest (.codex/skills.manifest) should track: installed skill names, versions/refs, source repositories, installation timestamps, and any skill-specific configuration. Provide functions for reading, writing, and querying the manifest.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:39.353063+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:47.633024+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.2","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:39.353773+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
{"id":"cc-skills-i97.3","title":"Implement submodule management","description":"Implement git submodule management for skill repositories. Handle adding skills as submodules, updating submodule refs, removing submodules cleanly, and syncing submodule state. Should integrate with the manifest to maintain consistency.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:40.514225+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:40.514225+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.3","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:40.515876+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
{"id":"cc-skills-i97.4","title":"Implement sparse-checkout management","description":"Implement sparse-checkout management for efficient skill installation. Only checkout the specific skill directories needed rather than entire repositories. Handle sparse-checkout initialization, pattern management, and cleanup when skills are removed.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:41.519863+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:41.519863+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.4","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:41.52149+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
{"id":"cc-skills-i97.5","title":"Add dirty state detection and blocking","description":"Implement detection of dirty git state (uncommitted changes, untracked files in skill areas). Block destructive operations (install, remove, sync) when the repository has uncommitted changes to prevent data loss. Provide clear error messages and --force flag for advanced users.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:42.259558+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:42.259558+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.5","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:42.261379+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
{"id":"cc-skills-i97.6","title":"Validate repo URL from trusted sources only","description":"Implement security validation for skill repository URLs. Maintain a configurable allowlist of trusted sources (e.g., github.com/anthropics/*). Reject installation from untrusted sources by default. Provide configuration option to add trusted sources and --trust flag for one-time overrides with appropriate warnings.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:43.055197+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:43.055197+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.6","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:30:43.05785+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
{"id":"cc-skills-i97.7","title":"Implement catalog command","description":"Implement the 'skillsctl catalog' command to list available skills from configured registries. Should display skill names, descriptions, categories, and compatibility info. Support filtering by category, searching by keyword, and different output formats (table, json).","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:02.202434+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:02.202434+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.7","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:02.203874+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
{"id":"cc-skills-i97.8","title":"Implement suggest command with scoring algorithm","description":"Implement the 'skillsctl suggest' command to recommend skills based on project context. Analyze project structure (package.json, Cargo.toml, etc.), existing tools, and file patterns to score and rank relevant skills. Display suggestions with confidence scores and explanations for why each skill was recommended.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:03.853204+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:03.853204+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.8","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:03.855754+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
{"id":"cc-skills-i97.9","title":"Implement install command (submodule + sparse-checkout)","description":"Implement the 'skillsctl install \u003cskill\u003e' command to install skills into the project. Use git submodules for repository management and sparse-checkout for efficient storage. Update manifest, validate source URL, check for dirty state, and handle conflicts with existing skills. Support version/ref specification.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"netmin@pm.me","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:05.268248+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D.","updated_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:05.268248+03:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"cc-skills-i97.9","depends_on_id":"cc-skills-i97","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-22T13:31:05.270555+03:00","created_by":"Vitaly D."}]}
